The paper discusses the development of a new architecture for artificial intelligence that is specifically designed for planning. This makes it likely that the paper would be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and robotics (cs.RO). Additionally, the paper applies the architecture to image-based tasks such as maze generation and pool simulation, which suggests that it could also be categorized under computer vision (cs.CV) and systems and control (cs.SY).
